data.description: Investor's Dream south of I-10, just 9 Miles to Duke Field and 20 to Eglin! Unlock the potential of this charming property for a great rental income opportunity! Possibilities are endless with an eat-in kitchen, a spacious den featuring a working fireplace and vaulted ceiling and a large fenced-in backyard, perfect for family activities and barbeques. Recent updates include a recently painted living room and newer vinyl floors (excluding bedrooms), complemented by new tile floors in the bathrooms. With a few touches and updates, this home presents an excellent opportunity for investors to possibly just apply some, mostly-cosmetic TLC. **Seller will consider conveying panels and replacing roof for the right offer. Otherwise, panels don't convey and roof is as is. Take note of a past cooking fire that left cosmetic damage in the kitchen area, necessitating paint and repairs. The oven may require replacement. Exercise caution on the deck, as railings are not yet completed. The HVAC has been maintained but the ages of it and the water heater are unknown but are working fine. Don't miss out on this investment gem - seize the opportunity for a profitable venture in a prime location!
